WEBVTT

00:15:31.097 --> 00:15:34.757
Can they recognize when a racial elephant
shows up in a room?

00:15:35.288 --> 00:15:38.556
Can they reduce
their tsunami interpretation

00:15:38.580 --> 00:15:40.751
down to a mountain-climbing adventure

00:15:40.775 --> 00:15:43.125
that they can engage and not run away?

00:15:43.568 --> 00:15:47.924
Can they make a healthy
and just decision in 60 seconds?

00:15:48.511 --> 00:15:49.694
Can I?

00:15:50.103 --> 00:15:51.270
Can you?

00:15:51.660 --> 00:15:53.189
Yes, we can.

00:15:53.955 --> 00:15:57.517
We can build healthier
relationships around race

00:15:57.541 --> 00:16:01.931
if we learn to calculate, locate
communicate, breathe and exhale